      <title>曼城的麻烦从英超联赛蔓延到政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/manchester-city-s-troubles-get-political-with-charges-verdict-looming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于面临 115 项违反财务规则的指控，该俱乐部糟糕的赛季可能会变得更糟。其影响将超出足球范围。 ]]></description>
